sys_hub_action_type_definition.description:
&amp;amp;lt;p&amp;amp;gt;Return the first User ID found based on the following search criteria.&amp;amp;lt;/p&amp;amp;gt;

&amp;amp;lt;p&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;b&amp;amp;gt;Inputs:&amp;amp;lt;/b&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;/p&amp;amp;gt;
&amp;amp;lt;ul&amp;amp;gt;
&amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;strong&amp;amp;gt;First Name&amp;amp;lt;/strong&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;/li&amp;amp;gt;
&amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;strong&amp;amp;gt;Last Name&amp;amp;lt;/strong&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;/li&amp;amp;gt;
&amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;strong&amp;amp;gt;Display Name&amp;amp;lt;/strong&amp;amp;gt; - Name displayed in the address book for the user.&amp;amp;lt;/li&amp;amp;gt;
&amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;strong&amp;amp;gt;User Login ID&amp;amp;lt;/strong&amp;amp;gt; - Login User ID is same as User Principal Name(UPN). &amp;amp;lt;strong&amp;amp;gt;Example:&amp;amp;lt;/strong&amp;amp;gt; johndoe@snc.com.&amp;amp;lt;/li&amp;amp;gt;
&amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;strong&amp;amp;gt;Email Alias&amp;amp;lt;/strong&amp;amp;gt; - Alias configured for an email account. A single email account can have more than one alias.&amp;amp;lt;/li&amp;amp;gt;
&amp;amp;lt;/ul&amp;amp;gt;

&amp;amp;lt;p&amp;amp;gt;At least one input is required. Using multiple inputs will help to narrow down the search.&amp;amp;lt;/p&amp;amp;gt;

&amp;amp;lt;p&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;b&amp;amp;gt;Outputs:&amp;amp;lt;/b&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;/p&amp;amp;gt;
&amp;amp;lt;ul&amp;amp;gt;
&amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;strong&amp;amp;gt;Status&amp;amp;lt;/strong&amp;amp;gt; - Will be set to &amp;amp;ldquo;User Found&amp;amp;quot; if a single user is found, &amp;amp;quot;User Not Found&amp;amp;quot; if no user is found, &amp;amp;quot;Multiple Users Found&amp;amp;quot; if multiple users are found matching the search criteria, or &amp;amp;ldquo;Error&amp;amp;quot; if a failure in Azure AD occurs.&amp;amp;lt;/li&amp;amp;gt;
&amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;strong&amp;amp;gt;User ID&amp;amp;lt;/strong&amp;amp;gt; -  First user found with matching criteria in Azure AD.&amp;amp;lt;/li&amp;amp;gt;
&amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;strong&amp;amp;gt;Error Message&amp;amp;lt;/strong&amp;amp;gt; - Reason for error. Populated only when an error occurs.&amp;amp;lt;/li&amp;amp;gt;
&amp;amp;lt;/ul&amp;amp;gt;

&amp;amp;lt;p&amp;amp;gt;The status will be Error only in case of any failure in Azure AD.&amp;amp;lt;/p&amp;amp;gt;

&amp;amp;lt;p&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;b&amp;amp;gt;Error Messages:&amp;amp;lt;/b&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;/p&amp;amp;gt; 
&amp;amp;lt;ul&amp;amp;gt;
&amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;gt;Something went wrong. Response was empty&amp;amp;lt;/li&amp;amp;gt;
&amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;gt;Unauthorized&amp;amp;lt;/li&amp;amp;gt;
&amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;gt;Set at least one of the properties - First Name/Last Name/Display Name/User Login ID/E-Mail Alias&amp;amp;lt;/li&amp;amp;gt;
&amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;gt;Insufficient Permissions. Please Check OAuth Token and scope permission&amp;amp;lt;/li&amp;amp;gt;
&amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;gt;Forbidden Request. Please Check OAuth Token and scope permission&amp;amp;lt;/li&amp;amp;gt;
&amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;gt;Invalid Connection&amp;amp;lt;/li&amp;amp;gt;
&amp;amp;lt;li&amp;amp;gt;Unknown Error&amp;amp;lt;/li&amp;amp;gt;
&amp;amp;lt;/ul&amp;amp;gt; 

&amp;amp;lt;p&amp;amp;gt;To use this action, a corresponding Azure AD connection and credential must be created and associated with the Azure AD Connection &amp;amp;amp; Credential alias. &amp;amp;lt;a target=&amp;amp;quot;_blank&amp;amp;quot;  href=&amp;amp;quot;http://docs.servicenow.com/?context=CSHelp:credentials-connections-alias&amp;amp;quot;&amp;amp;gt;Learn More&amp;amp;lt;/a&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;/p&amp;amp;gt; 

&amp;amp;lt;p&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;b&amp;amp;gt;Note&amp;amp;lt;/b&amp;amp;gt;: Requires a subscription for production use. &amp;amp;lt;a target=&amp;amp;quot;_blank&amp;amp;quot; href=&amp;amp;quot;https://docs.servicenow.com/?context=CSHelp:IntegrationHub-licensing-information&amp;amp;quot;&amp;amp;gt;Read More&amp;amp;lt;/a&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;lt;/p&amp;amp;gt;
